Text.string: I require your help, Vault Hunter.
Let's build a cannon!
That's it! You're doing it!
Keep them coming, Vault Hunter!
Vault Hunter, your killing skills are delicious to behold.
I have no mouth and I must salivate.
I almost feel bad for those Guardians... It's not their fault they're like this.
Quiet, Sparrow! They're mindless constructs. End of story.
Well done, well done. Now I require parts from Maliwan vehicles. A stabilizer from a cyclone and a shock absorber from an outrunner shall suffice.
Wow. I don't know how you do it, Vault Hunter. But I'm glad I'm on your side!
Just because YOU'RE a craven simpleton doesn't mean everyone's like you.
More like “craven” some tasty marshmallows!

Typhon began work on a prototype defensive cannon. We're going to finish it so you can put the hurt on those Maliwan putzes. To get it firing, we're going to need some captive Guardian energy. First, take this energy trap.
I dream of killing you.
Those things look so fun. I wish I could drive one. No! BE one.
You barely fulfill your primary function. As a vehicle, you would be a miserable failure.
Looks like you've gathered all the parts. Return to me, and we will assemble our dark cannon.
Hell yeah, new cannon!
I do love a good cannon.
Ah, a new weapon of war for the hunt.
Always love a new cannon!
Now place the parts you gathered, and set up the energy trap near the prototype.
Careful. That energy is volatile.
Oh no! OH NO! It looks like it's gonna blow! Back up!
False alarm!
Yes, somehow we survived the bright light. Here you go, Vault Hunter! Our dark cannon beckons.
We're gonna use Guardian energy to power the cannon! It's gonna look so cool! We'll just shoot it into the sky and not hurt anyone!
It is beautiful. So dark. And so cannon. Your payment, Vault Hunter.

Well, what are you waiting for? You've got a fancy new dark cannon, don't you? Get out there and kill some Maliwan, you force of nature. You freaking king of the jungle. You beautiful monster. Boom boom, baby.
I will shoot my new weapon where I please. Vault Hunter, you'll use the energy trap to capture the Guardian energy. Now head to the Temple!
Placing the energy trap will trigger aggression in any Guardians nearby. Place that trap, then lock and load.
Here they come! Be careful!
They don't need to be “careful”, they need to be “badass”.
They can be both!
Careful is for wimps.
All I ever need to be is badass. Full stop.
The hunt is on.
Careful was my old middle name. Then it got killed. Good riddance!
